# Templ8

A powerful, extensible templating engine.

## Status

| Source     | Shields                                                                                                                         |
| ---------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| Project    | ![release][release_shield] ![license][license_shield]  ![lines][lines_shield] ![languages][languages_shield]                    |
